[en_US]
Overall/Super Luigi Bros. 3 (35th Anniversary)

Hack by Mario_GMD

Date 2020-08-15

Description:
The second hack rom of SMB3 but with luigi celebrating the 35th anniversary, this time the player has the mission to rescue Princess Daisy from the clutches of the evil Bowser (the same story from the original SMB3 but replacing Mario with Luigi and Peach with Daisy).

This patch aims to change the green Mario sprites to Luigi’s design from the SMB3 of SNES, preserving the essence of the original game,this hack rom comes from the 35th anniversary of SMB but with Luigi.

The designs were changed to give it greater and better visual and aesthetic quality (avoiding a green Mario and a yellow Peach). Credits to the creators of the sheets sprites of Luigi & Daisy.



